1 This act would allow a one-time non-refundable tax credit for the actual costs of connecting
2 a single family or multi-family dwelling to a municipal sewer system to the owner of the real
3 property credited to the owner's personal income tax or corporate income tax based on the filing
4 status of the owner.
5 This act would take effect upon passage.
